headline: Jack Henry's Symitar Solidifies Position as the Leading Platform for Credit Unions
summary: Callahan & Associates, a leading data and consulting firm in the credit union industry, confirmed Jack Henry's Symitar platform as the top platform for credit unions in its annual ranking of financial technology providers. Symitar® has been listed as the top platform every year since 2018.
